  <entry>
    <title>markdown</title>
    <link href="https://oops-re.github.io/2021/11/17/markdown/"/>
    <id>https://oops-re.github.io/2021/11/17/markdown/</id>
    <published>2021-11-17T10:35:31.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-11-17T10:36:29.252Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="markdown语法学习"><a href="#markdown语法学习" class="headerlink" title="markdown语法学习"></a>markdown语法学习</h1><h2 id="1-标题语法："><a href="#1-标题语法：" class="headerlink" title="1.标题语法："></a>1.标题语法：</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//&quot;#&quot;一个＃字键叫一个空格分开，输入内容，该内容将被加粗加大到最大</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//“##”二级变大</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//“###”三级变大</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//通常用作目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 加粗加大到最大 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 加粗加大到第二大 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">### 加粗加大到第三大 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例：</p><h1 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h1><h2 id="标题-1"><a href="#标题-1" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><h3 id="标题-2"><a href="#标题-2" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h3><h4 id="标题-3"><a href="#标题-3" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h4><h2 id="2-字体："><a href="#2-字体：" class="headerlink" title="2.字体："></a>2.字体：</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//加粗</span></span><br><span class="line">**加粗内容**</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//代码高亮</span></span><br><span class="line">==<span class="keyword">int</span> main==</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//删除线</span></span><br><span class="line">~~删除内容~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//斜体</span></span><br><span class="line">*斜体内容*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>加粗内容</strong></p><p>==高亮==</p><p><del>删除内容</del><br><em>斜体内容</em></p><h2 id="3-引用"><a href="#3-引用" class="headerlink" title="3.引用"></a>3.引用</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//引用语法：</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;名字：</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;年龄：</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;作者：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>名字：</p><blockquote><p>年龄：</p></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><p>作者：</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h2 id="4-分割线"><a href="#4-分割线" class="headerlink" title="4.分割线"></a>4.分割线</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//分割线语法：</span></span><br><span class="line">---分割线<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">***分割线<span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>//—</p><hr><p>//***</p><hr><h2 id="5-插入图片"><a href="#5-插入图片" class="headerlink" title="5.插入图片"></a>5.插入图片</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//在线图片</span></span><br><span class="line">![图片名字](图片地址)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//本地图片</span></span><br><span class="line">![图片名字](图片路径)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616578274010-0ddd36f1417f?ixid=MXwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHw=&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="在线图片"></p><p>![本地图片](C:\Users\86182\Documents\Tencent Files\1411495649\FileRecv\屏幕截图 2021-01-24 231116.png)</p><h2 id="6-超链接"><a href="#6-超链接" class="headerlink" title="6.超链接"></a>6.超链接</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//超链接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span>行内式：</span><br><span class="line">这是一个[链接](这里写地址<span class="string">&quot;这里会有一个显示,可加可不加&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span>参考式：（很少写，一般用于学术发表）</span><br><span class="line">学代码一般在[bilibili][<span class="number">1</span>]、[CSDN][<span class="number">2</span>]、[菜鸟][<span class="number">3</span>].</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">1</span>]:https:<span class="comment">//www.bilibili.com/&quot;bilibili&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">2</span>]:https:<span class="comment">//www.csdn.net/&quot;SCDN&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="number">3</span>]:https:<span class="comment">//www.runoob.com/&quot;菜鸟&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span>自动链接</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;https:<span class="comment">//www.runoob.com/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="number">1411495649</span><span class="meta">@qq</span>.com&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>//超链接<br>1.行内式：<br>这是一个<a href="//www.runoob.com/%22%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA,%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%8A%A0%22">链接</a></p><p>2.参考式</p><p>学代码一般在<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/" title="bilibili">bilibili</a>、<a href="https://www.csdn.net/" title="SCDN">CSDN</a>、<a href="https://www.runoob.com/" title="菜鸟">菜鸟</a>.</p><p>3.自动链接<br>    <a href="https://www.runoob.com/">https://www.runoob.com/</a><br>    <a href="mailto:&#49;&#x34;&#x31;&#49;&#52;&#x39;&#53;&#x36;&#52;&#57;&#x40;&#113;&#113;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#109;">&#49;&#x34;&#x31;&#49;&#52;&#x39;&#53;&#x36;&#52;&#57;&#x40;&#113;&#113;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#109;</a></p><h2 id="7-打表"><a href="#7-打表" class="headerlink" title="7.打表"></a>7.打表</h2><p>使用快捷键</p><table><thead><tr><th>姓名</th><th>柒</th><th>玉</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>成绩</strong></td><td>123</td><td>12</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="结束markdown学习"><a href="#结束markdown学习" class="headerlink" title="结束markdown学习"></a>结束markdown学习</h1><p>！！！</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
